-- SMA Says Founders, Main Stockholders Transfer Some Stock to Family Members
-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 2010-10-01T10:35:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-01/sma-says-founders-main-stockholders-transfer-some-stock-to-family-members.html
SMA Solar Technology AG said the
company’s four founders and main shareholders have transferred
“parts of their shares” to family members of the next
generation. For at least seven years, 25.2 percent of SMA’s
shares will be concentrated in a pool agreement, according to a
statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Gavin at 
 mgavin2@bloomberg.net  